Environment setup
=================

In the tt directory:
make init

You also need to have CouchDB up and running in your machine.

To compile the source code of the tt application:
make compile


CouchDB objects
===============

scores: nick x scores
matches: winner x looser x figures x gsec


CouchDB views:
==============

tt/scores:
----------
function(doc) {morgon
  if (doc.type == "score")
    emit(doc.score, {nick:doc.nick, score:doc.score});
}

tt/matches:
-----------
function(doc) {
  if (doc.type == "match")
    emit(doc.gsec, {winner:doc.winner, looser:doc.looser, figures:doc.figures, gsec:doc.gsec});
}



